Ten tubers are worth only Rs. 10,000 (75 cents).
Economic disparities between indigenous papuas and new migrants have increased over time and have arrived in large numbers since the introduction of new flights to Nabire Airport.
Few existing jobs are usually available to better educated and wealthy migrants.
Dads rarely have the money or the necessary skills to run their own competitive business.
